<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Support</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .support-container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .support-container h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .support-container p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .support-container a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            display: block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .support-container a:hover {
            background-color: #d6d8db;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="support-container">
        <h2>Support</h2>
        <p>If you need help with your login details, please contact our support team:</p>
        <p>Email: support@trustbank.com</p>
        <p>Phone: +123 456 7890</p>
        <a href="/homepage">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
